	 We use a "strict" DTD to make IE follow the alignment rules. -->
	 
<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd">
<head>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${context:css/examples/localization.css}"/>
